      "date": "2013-08-06 00:22:06.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 2: Verified\n\nTests received by maloo, run on CentOS release 6.4/x86_64: (https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/a75e95a6-fe2b-11e2-9fd5-52540035b04c).  Ran 14 tests.  No failures.",
